This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of Natural Language Processing (NLP) and specifically in the area of paraphrase generation. Therefore, cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely sub-category. Additionally, the paper proposes a new method that extends neural machine translation (NMT) models, which falls under the sub-categories of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also evaluates its proposed method using a new evaluation metric, which could fall under the sub-category of cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Finally, the paper focuses on the diversity aspect of paraphrase generation, which could also fall under the sub-category of cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
